    {
      "type": "legacySection",
      "id": "conceitos-chave",
      "title": "üß≠ Conceitos-chave",
      "html": "<!-- Each term uses a compact card style --> <div data-legacy-card=\"\"> <article> <h3>Throughput</h3> <p> Taxa de sa√≠da do sistema (itens/unidade de tempo). Em log√≠stica, pedidos despachados por hora. </p> </article> <article> <h3>Lead Time</h3> <p> Tempo total ‚Äúpedido‚Üíentrega‚Äù. Inclui esperas, filas e processamento. </p> </article> <article> <h3> WIP (Trabalho em Progresso) </h3> <p> Itens em processamento. Excesso de WIP aumenta filas e lead time. </p> </article> <article> <h3>Gargalo</h3> <p> Etapa que limita o throughput do sistema. Otimiza√ß√µes fora do gargalo t√™m pouco efeito. </p> </article> <article> <h3>OTIF / Fill Rate</h3> <p> On-Time In-Full e taxa de atendimento. Medem efic√°cia do fluxo fim-a-fim. </p> </article> <article> <h3>Feedback &amp; Homeostase</h3> <p> Loops que estabilizam (negativo) ou amplificam (positivo) o comportamento do sistema. </p> </article> </div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "legacySection",
      "id": "sipoc-vsm",
      "title": "üìã SIPOC + Mini VSM",
      "html": "<figure> <!-- Accessible inline SVG diagram --> <svg viewBox=\"0 0 1000 280\" role=\"img\" aria-labelledby=\"sipocTitle sipocDesc\"> <title id=\"sipocTitle\">Diagrama SIPOC + Mini VSM</title> <desc id=\"sipocDesc\"> Fornecedores, Entradas, Processo, Sa√≠das, Clientes e tempos de espera/processamento. </desc> <!-- Boxes --> <!-- NOTE: Using basic shapes for clarity; labels are high-contrast --> <rect x=\"20\" y=\"20\" width=\"160\" height=\"80\" rx=\"12\" fill=\"#e0f2fe\" stroke=\"#38bdf8\"></rect> <text x=\"100\" y=\"65\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" fill=\"#0c4a6e\"> Fornecedores </text> <rect x=\"200\" y=\"20\" width=\"160\" height=\"80\" rx=\"12\" fill=\"#ecfeff\" stroke=\"#06b6d4\"></rect> <text x=\"280\" y=\"65\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" fill=\"#0e7490\"> Entradas </text> <rect x=\"380\" y=\"20\" width=\"240\" height=\"80\" rx=\"12\" fill=\"#f0f9ff\" stroke=\"#7dd3fc\"></rect> <text x=\"500\" y=\"55\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" fill=\"#0369a1\"> Processo </text> <text x=\"500\" y=\"75\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#0369a1\"> P1 ‚Üí P2 ‚Üí P3 (gargalo em P2) </text> <rect x=\"640\" y=\"20\" width=\"160\" height=\"80\" rx=\"12\" fill=\"#f0fdf4\" stroke=\"#6ee7b7\"></rect> <text x=\"720\" y=\"65\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" fill=\"#065f46\"> Sa√≠das </text> <rect x=\"820\" y=\"20\" width=\"160\" height=\"80\" rx=\"12\" fill=\"#fef9c3\" stroke=\"#f59e0b\"></rect> <text x=\"900\" y=\"65\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" fill=\"#92400e\"> Clientes </text> <!-- Flow arrows --> <line x1=\"180\" y1=\"60\" x2=\"200\" y2=\"60\" stroke=\"#64748b\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"></line> <line x1=\"360\" y1=\"60\" x2=\"380\" y2=\"60\" stroke=\"#64748b\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"></line> <line x1=\"620\" y1=\"60\" x2=\"640\" y2=\"60\" stroke=\"#64748b\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"></line> <line x1=\"800\" y1=\"60\" x2=\"820\" y2=\"60\" stroke=\"#64748b\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"></line> <!-- Mini VSM timing bars under the process --> <rect x=\"380\" y=\"130\" width=\"70\" height=\"14\" fill=\"#94a3b8\"></rect> <text x=\"415\" y=\"160\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#334155\"> Espera 2m </text> <rect x=\"455\" y=\"130\" width=\"50\" height=\"14\" fill=\"#22c55e\"></rect> <text x=\"480\" y=\"160\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#166534\"> Proc. 1m </text> <rect x=\"510\" y=\"130\" width=\"90\" height=\"14\" fill=\"#94a3b8\"></rect> <text x=\"555\" y=\"160\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#334155\"> Espera 3m </text> <rect x=\"605\" y=\"130\" width=\"60\" height=\"14\" fill=\"#22c55e\"></rect> <text x=\"635\" y=\"160\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#166534\"> Proc. 1m </text> <!-- Arrow marker definition --> <defs> <marker id=\"arrow\" markerWidth=\"8\" markerHeight=\"8\" refX=\"6\" refY=\"4\" orient=\"auto-start-reverse\"> <path d=\"M0,0 L0,8 L8,4 z\" fill=\"#64748b\"></path> </marker> </defs> </svg> <figcaption> SIPOC para leitura sist√™mica + Mini VSM destacando esperas (cinza) e processamento (verde). </figcaption> </figure> <div data-legacy-card=\"\"> <ul> <li> <strong>Onde a informa√ß√£o vira a√ß√£o?</strong> No gatilho do pedido (ERP/WMS), que movimenta picking/packing (fluxo de materiais). </li> <li> <strong>Como reduzir lead time?</strong> Diminuindo esperas (filas), equilibrando WIP e aliviando o gargalo. </li> </ul> </div>"
