      "html": "<!-- Use radio buttons for accessibility --> <form id=\"quizForm\" data-quiz-answers=\"{&quot;q1&quot;:&quot;B&quot;,&quot;q2&quot;:&quot;B&quot;,&quot;q3&quot;:&quot;B&quot;,&quot;q4&quot;:&quot;B&quot;,&quot;q5&quot;:&quot;B&quot;}\" data-quiz-button=\"#submitQuiz\" data-quiz-score=\"#quizScore\"> <!-- Q1 --> <fieldset> <legend> 1) Se o WIP aumenta sem ampliar capacidade, o que tende a ocorrer? </legend> <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"A\"> A) Throughput aumenta proporcionalmente</label> <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"B\"> B) Lead time tende a aumentar</label> <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"C\"> C) Gargalo desaparece</label> <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"D\"> D) OTIF aumenta automaticamente</label> <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"E\"> E) Nada muda</label> </fieldset> <!-- Q2 --> <fieldset> <legend> 2) Em um sistema aberto, o que melhor representa feedback negativo? </legend> <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"A\"> A) Promo√ß√£o viral que aumenta demanda sem limite</label> <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"B\"> B) Controle de estoque que reduz compras quando h√° excesso</label> <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"C\"> C) Falha em cascata na rede</label> <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"D\"> D) Automa√ß√£o que duplica ordens</label> <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"E\"> E) Atraso fixo em transporte</label> </fieldset> <!-- Q3 --> <fieldset> <legend> 3) OTIF mede principalmente: </legend> <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"A\"> A) Utiliza√ß√£o de CPU</label> <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"B\"> B) Entregas no prazo e completas</label> <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"C\"> C) Tamanho do lote</label> <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"D\"> D) Custos de picking</label> <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"E\"> E) Invent√°ri